It was the evil tai sui's fault!

00:50:30.720 --> 00:50:32.520
Shuang'er became the catalyst!

00:50:41.560 --> 00:50:43.120
Shuang'er!

00:50:49.360 --> 00:50:50.720
Shuang'er!

00:50:51.080 --> 00:50:52.480
Shuang'er!

00:50:54.640 --> 00:50:56.440
Dahan-dahang maglakad!

00:50:56.840 --> 00:50:58.280
Hanapin ang iyong kapatid

00:50:58.520 --> 00:50:59.880
Bilisan mo bumalik!

00:50:59.880 --> 00:51:02.240
Father will wait for you at home!

00:51:02.480 --> 00:51:04.320
I'll wait in the village

00:51:04.680 --> 00:51:06.640
Wait for the relief grain from the city!

00:51:06.800 --> 00:51:08.640
Ngunit hindi ito dumating!

00:51:08.760 --> 00:51:09.720
Ang mga taganayon

00:51:09.720 --> 00:51:11.720
One by one, they died of illness.

00:51:12.520 --> 00:51:14.800
Ako lang ang nakaligtas.

00:51:15.080 --> 00:51:16.360
Anong kasalanan!

00:51:17.040 --> 00:51:18.840
Strange illness everywhere!

00:51:19.120 --> 00:51:20.160
Ang matandang ito

00:51:20.680 --> 00:51:21.760
Wala akong pupuntahan!

00:51:21.960 --> 00:51:25.520
I have to wait for my ling'er and shuang'er!

00:51:27.160 --> 00:51:29.240
Bibilhan kita ng pagkain!

00:51:29.680 --> 00:51:32.480
It's all meat left by the mountain god!

00:51:49.600 --> 00:51:50.800
Akala ko

00:51:51.200 --> 00:51:52.600
Walang butil na natitira,

00:51:53.200 --> 00:51:54.920
Where did the meat come from?

00:52:17.640 --> 00:52:18.400
Halika

00:52:19.200 --> 00:52:20.320
Warm yourself by the fire.

00:52:21.760 --> 00:52:24.200
Magluluto ako ng karne para sa iyo!

00:52:28.840 --> 00:52:30.040
Ito ay

00:52:30.360 --> 00:52:31.440
Karne ng fox!

00:52:32.880 --> 00:52:35.320
Masarap ang karne ng lobo!

00:52:36.120 --> 00:52:37.400
Ang aming nayon

00:52:38.720 --> 00:52:40.400
Ito ay puno ng mga fox!

00:52:40.560 --> 00:52:41.960
Walang natira,

00:52:41.960 --> 00:52:45.080
Foxes run wild everywhere!

00:52:45.080 --> 00:52:48.080
Later, i'll take you to the side hall

00:52:48.280 --> 00:52:51.240
I caught many foxes there.

00:52:51.760 --> 00:52:52.600
Sapat na kumain!

00:52:53.600 --> 00:52:54.520
Tama na!

00:52:55.160 --> 00:52:56.880
Walang relief grain

00:52:57.280 --> 00:52:58.480
Ayos lang.

00:52:58.880 --> 00:53:01.120
This old man will eat fox meat!

00:53:06.280 --> 00:53:08.640
This fox meat has it been left out too long?

00:53:08.680 --> 00:53:09.840
Malamig ang panahon.

00:53:10.520 --> 00:53:11.640
Ang karne na ito

00:53:12.240 --> 00:53:13.680
Hindi ito madaling masira.

00:53:13.720 --> 00:53:14.960
Inihaw itong mabuti

00:53:15.600 --> 00:53:16.800
Nakakain pa!

00:53:54.240 --> 00:53:55.480
Karne ng lobo!

00:53:55.480 --> 00:53:57.680
Ang lahat ng ito ay karne ng fox!

00:54:00.800 --> 00:54:01.600
Ang mga ito

00:54:02.120 --> 00:54:03.440
Ano ang mga bagay na ito?

00:54:04.320 --> 00:54:06.600
This is old cheng's whole family.

00:54:07.280 --> 00:54:08.680
Ito ang ina ni gouqi.

00:54:08.680 --> 00:54:10.960
This is old lame and his brother.

00:54:12.480 --> 00:54:13.720
Kailangan kong mabuhay.

00:54:14.480 --> 00:54:18.160
I have to wait for my ling'er and shuang'er!

00:54:18.400 --> 00:54:21.000
There's nothing left to eat in the village.

00:54:21.280 --> 00:54:23.280
Tanging karne ng fox ang natitira!

00:54:23.280 --> 00:54:24.040
Baliw ka!

00:54:24.040 --> 00:54:25.240
You're the one who's crazy!

00:54:26.480 --> 00:54:28.200
Tanging karne ng fox ang natitira!

00:54:28.280 --> 00:54:30.120
Didn't you want to eat fox meat?

00:54:51.320 --> 00:54:52.720
As soon as i fled back to chang'an,

00:54:53.000 --> 00:54:54.120
Sinabi ko sa ministro

00:54:54.120 --> 00:54:55.840
About this terrible incident.

00:54:56.480 --> 00:54:57.560
Ngunit sa chang'an,

00:54:58.320 --> 00:55:00.880
Refugees from huazhou had already arrived.

00:55:00.880 --> 00:55:02.760
The city was already in chaos.

00:55:03.080 --> 00:55:05.160
Walang pakialam sa lahat.

00:55:05.760 --> 00:55:07.000
So ibig sabihin

00:55:07.000 --> 00:55:08.520
Patay na rin si old man wu?

00:55:08.640 --> 00:55:09.840
Wala na lahat.

00:55:09.840 --> 00:55:12.400
The whole family is wiped out.

00:55:12.480 --> 00:55:14.200
Then what on earth is

00:55:14.200 --> 00:55:15.720
Haunting us in the middle of the night?

00:55:15.840 --> 00:55:16.640
Lord chen,

00:55:17.080 --> 00:55:18.120
Sa tingin mo

00:55:18.120 --> 00:55:19.920
It could be wu shuang turned evil spirit?

00:55:20.720 --> 00:55:22.920
Now huang chao's army has reached tongguan.

00:55:23.120 --> 00:55:24.720
The world is filled with hostility.

00:55:25.800 --> 00:55:27.360
Hindi imposible

00:55:27.720 --> 00:55:29.480
For the dead to return to life!

00:55:29.480 --> 00:55:31.320
General tian and i both saw it.

00:55:31.320 --> 00:55:33.480
Can it be that both of us were hallucinating?

00:55:38.760 --> 00:55:39.400
Hindi.

00:55:39.760 --> 00:55:40.640
Hindi.

00:55:40.920 --> 00:55:42.600
Something's wrong with the air.

00:55:43.320 --> 00:55:44.400
My whole body feels weak,

00:55:44.600 --> 00:55:45.960
Like my bones have been pulled out.

00:55:45.960 --> 00:55:47.000
Parang

00:55:47.000 --> 00:55:49.760
Someone drugged me with muscle-relaxing powder.

00:55:51.280 --> 00:55:54.240
It must be wu shuang's ghost come to avenge you!

00:55:54.480 --> 00:55:55.600
Namatay siya nang mali.

00:55:55.600 --> 00:55:57.360
What's that got to do with me?

00:55:57.360 --> 00:55:58.360
Tumahimik ka!

00:55:58.360 --> 00:55:59.920
How dare the spirit of a dead prisoner

00:55:59.920 --> 00:56:01.880
Cause trouble in front of me?

00:56:02.080 --> 00:56:03.560
She was beheaded with a ghost-headed saber.

00:56:03.560 --> 00:56:04.840
How could she return to life?

00:56:04.840 --> 00:56:08.080
Who says beheaded people can't come back?

00:56:21.200 --> 00:56:22.480
What kind of creature are you?

00:56:22.880 --> 00:56:24.320
Daring to kidnap lord tian?

00:56:25.280 --> 00:56:26.840
Do you know who my adoptive father is?

00:56:26.840 --> 00:56:28.680
My adoptive father is eunuch tian zhengyi!

00:56:29.160 --> 00:56:30.400
Bitawan mo ako agad!

00:56:30.640 --> 00:56:31.440
Kung hindi,

00:56:31.440 --> 00:56:32.640
Kukunin kita

00:56:32.640 --> 00:56:34.280
Pinutol-putol!

00:56:34.360 --> 00:56:35.320
Immortal master, spare me!

00:56:35.880 --> 00:56:38.240
Ang opisyal na ito ay si yang zhizhi, bise ministro ng kita.

00:56:38.400 --> 00:56:40.680
I only calculate grain and silver in the yamen.

00:56:40.680 --> 00:56:42.200
I've never harmed anyone!

00:56:42.200 --> 00:56:43.360
You must have arrested the wrong person!

00:56:43.440 --> 00:56:45.880
I've never had any dealings with the wu family!

00:56:46.320 --> 00:56:48.080
Your excellency, if you want money,

00:56:48.080 --> 00:56:50.480
Ang matandang ito ay handang mag-alok ng isang libong tael ng ginto!

00:56:53.120 --> 00:56:54.720
Ayoko ng pera.

00:56:54.720 --> 00:56:56.920
I want the lives of the three of you.

00:57:14.720 --> 00:57:16.120
Ito ay... Ito ay...

00:57:16.120 --> 00:57:17.680
What are you yelling about?

00:57:19.800 --> 00:57:21.400
It's not me who wants to kill you.

00:57:21.960 --> 00:57:23.840
It's the death row prisoner you mentioned

00:57:23.840 --> 00:57:26.000
Who wants to settle blood debts.

00:57:26.840 --> 00:57:29.080
Are you talking about that wu shuang?

00:57:30.600 --> 00:57:31.280
Pero siya...

00:57:31.280 --> 00:57:33.240
She clearly was already...

00:57:34.640 --> 00:57:36.000
You chopped off her head,

00:57:36.000 --> 00:57:37.680
But i stitched her body back together.

00:57:39.000 --> 00:57:40.880
That day, old man wu held her corpse

00:57:40.880 --> 00:57:43.120
At lumuhod sa pintuan ko, yumuko hanggang sa dumugo ang ulo niya,

00:57:43.120 --> 00:57:44.400
Begging me to mend her body.

00:57:44.600 --> 00:57:46.080
The evil things in this temple

00:57:46.080 --> 00:57:47.960
Turned her into a fierce ghost.

00:57:47.960 --> 00:57:50.520
She forced me to use the three of your lives

00:57:50.520 --> 00:57:52.280
To make three body vessels

00:57:52.440 --> 00:57:55.120
Upang ibalik ang kanilang buong pamilya mula sa underworld.

00:57:55.640 --> 00:57:56.640
Ibig mong sabihin

00:57:56.880 --> 00:57:58.560
She turned into a fierce ghost?

00:57:58.560 --> 00:57:59.280
Nasaan siya?

00:57:59.920 --> 00:58:01.120
Right here in this temple.

00:58:02.720 --> 00:58:03.640
Immortal master,

00:58:03.640 --> 00:58:04.840
Patawarin mo ako!

00:58:05.080 --> 00:58:07.240
I have nothing to do with that witch!

00:58:07.560 --> 00:58:08.960
She must have arrested the wrong person!

00:58:08.960 --> 00:58:10.000
Huwag kang mag-alala.

00:58:11.120 --> 00:58:12.360
Huwag kang mag-alala.

00:58:12.600 --> 00:58:14.560
The body vessel ritual will start soon.

00:58:14.760 --> 00:58:16.120
Buong pamilya mo

00:58:16.120 --> 00:58:18.240
Can return to the mortal world!

00:58:18.360 --> 00:58:18.960
Ako...

00:58:18.960 --> 00:58:20.240
Ako... Ako...

00:58:51.280 --> 00:58:54.360
One talisman stabilizes the cosmos!

00:58:54.360 --> 00:58:55.480
Espirituwal na altar,

00:58:55.480 --> 00:58:56.400
Tumaas!

00:59:08.160 --> 00:59:10.040
Mga multo ng fengdu,

00:59:10.040 --> 00:59:11.600
Pakinggan mo ang utos ko!

00:59:12.040 --> 00:59:13.240
Magmartsa pasulong!

00:59:20.520 --> 00:59:22.960
Lumayo ka! lumayo ka!

00:59:23.520 --> 00:59:24.960
Immortal master, save me!

00:59:25.200 --> 00:59:26.200
Nagkamali ako!

00:59:26.200 --> 00:59:27.360
I didn't mean to kill him!

00:59:27.400 --> 00:59:29.560
Hindi ko talaga sinasadya!

00:59:32.560 --> 00:59:33.320
Kamahalan,

00:59:33.920 --> 00:59:35.280
Kung ililibre mo ako,

00:59:35.400 --> 00:59:36.360
Itong matandang lalaki

00:59:36.360 --> 00:59:37.920
Is willing to add another five thousand taels!

00:59:38.280 --> 00:59:40.400
Gold ingots hidden in nanshan grotto!

00:59:42.000 --> 00:59:43.360
Limang libong taels?

00:59:43.560 --> 00:59:45.120
Why should i believe you?

00:59:45.480 --> 00:59:46.720
Paano ito?

00:59:46.720 --> 00:59:47.960
Let me go alone to fetch it,

00:59:49.000 --> 00:59:50.880
And leave these two as hostages.

00:59:50.920 --> 00:59:51.840
Paano iyon tunog?

00:59:52.200 --> 00:59:53.560
Chen weishan!

00:59:53.560 --> 00:59:54.920
Ikaw na matandang hamak!

00:59:55.000 --> 00:59:56.480
Trying to sell me out to save your own skin?

00:59:56.720 --> 00:59:57.520
Sa tingin mo

00:59:57.520 --> 00:59:59.440
I don't know about all your dirty deeds?

00:59:59.440 --> 01:00:01.040
Since you've hidden so many gold ingots,

01:00:01.120 --> 01:00:01.800
Aalis na ako,

01:00:01.800 --> 01:00:03.480
I'll tell eunuch tian to seize your home first!

01:00:03.480 --> 01:00:04.560
Tian jinxiao!

01:00:05.080 --> 01:00:06.680
Nilustay mo ang mga damit panglamig ng border army,

01:00:06.680 --> 01:00:09.280
Dahilan upang mamatay ang daan-daang sundalo sa tongguan!

01:00:09.280 --> 01:00:10.600
If this gets to the lieutenant,

01:00:10.600 --> 01:00:12.840
Sa tingin mo ba mapoprotektahan ka ng adoptive father mo?

01:00:12.840 --> 01:00:13.640
Kalokohan!

01:00:13.640 --> 01:00:15.600
Sa panahon ng salot na balang huazhou, nagsumbong ka sa korte

01:00:15.600 --> 01:00:16.760
Na ang mga tao ay namumuhay sa kapayapaan at kasaganaan!

01:00:16.760 --> 01:00:17.960
Kung ito ay lumabas,

01:00:17.960 --> 01:00:19.200
Sa tingin mo ba ay ililigtas ka ng tatlong judicial bodies?

01:00:19.240 --> 01:00:20.680
Heneral tian, ​​

01:00:20.840 --> 01:00:22.760
Ingatan mo ang iyong mga salita! panoorin ang iyong mga salita!

01:00:22.760 --> 01:00:24.960
Both you and lord chen, say less!

01:00:24.960 --> 01:00:26.240
Bah, yang!

01:00:26.320 --> 01:00:27.560
Do you think i believe that

01:00:27.560 --> 01:00:29.200
Nonsense about the tai sui you made up?

01:00:29.400 --> 01:00:31.160
Halimaw kang walang puso!

01:00:31.160 --> 01:00:32.360
Dapat ikaw yan

01:00:32.360 --> 01:00:34.480
Na nalustay ang relief grain para kay wujia gou,

01:00:34.480 --> 01:00:36.520
Triggering the great plague in huazhou!

01:00:36.520 --> 01:00:38.400
Tian jinxiao, stop pretending to be moral!

01:00:38.560 --> 01:00:39.960
Wu ling was your personal soldier,

01:00:39.960 --> 01:00:41.040
Obeying your every order.

01:00:41.200 --> 01:00:43.320
Do you really think he dared

01:00:43.320 --> 01:00:45.280
Ang magnakaw ng pera sa mga patay nang wala ang iyong utos?

01:00:45.280 --> 01:00:46.760
At least i'm better than you!

01:00:46.760 --> 01:00:49.120
You tried to seize miss wu shuang,

01:00:49.120 --> 01:00:50.360
Assaulted her while drunk,

01:00:50.360 --> 01:00:51.600
And when she fought back desperately,

01:00:51.600 --> 01:00:53.600
You smashed her head with an ink slab!

01:00:53.600 --> 01:00:55.480
Pagkatapos ay ginawa mong baguhin ng coroner ang ulat ng autopsy,

01:00:55.920 --> 01:00:57.320
Tinatawag siyang mangkukulam!

01:00:57.320 --> 01:00:59.880
Do you think i have no connections in huazhou?

01:01:00.400 --> 01:01:02.240
Tumigil sa pagtatalo! tumigil sa pagtatalo!

01:01:02.440 --> 01:01:03.920
We're all in the same boat.

01:01:03.920 --> 01:01:05.680
None of us have clean hands!

01:01:05.840 --> 01:01:07.800
This isn't the time to settle scores!

01:01:07.800 --> 01:01:08.960
Someone else holds our weaknesses,

01:01:08.960 --> 01:01:10.680
Kaya lang wala ni isa sa amin ang naglakas loob na ilantad ito kanina!

01:01:10.680 --> 01:01:12.280
Putulin ang pagkukunwari!

01:01:12.280 --> 01:01:14.360
Tian, ​​naglakas loob kang imbestigahan ako sa likod ko,

01:01:14.360 --> 01:01:15.360
Pakana laban sa akin!

01:01:15.360 --> 01:01:16.760
Hinding hindi kita mapapatawad!

01:01:16.760 --> 01:01:17.360
Tama na!

01:01:17.360 --> 01:01:17.960
Ikaw...

01:01:20.520 --> 01:01:22.680
Mukhang hindi na natin kailangan ang mga ghost messenger para kumilos.

01:01:23.040 --> 01:01:26.040
Ikaw na mismo ang nagbuhos ng lahat ng iyong mga krimen!

01:01:26.600 --> 01:01:28.000
What trick are you playing?

01:01:39.120 --> 01:01:40.480
Sa tingin ko may isang tao

01:01:41.320 --> 01:01:44.200
Is watching the show in secret!

01:01:48.280 --> 01:01:49.400
Wang shao!

01:01:50.080 --> 01:01:53.200
So it's you, this jinwu guard dog, who set the trap!

01:01:53.200 --> 01:01:55.040
Bastard, bitawan mo ako!

01:01:55.040 --> 01:01:56.600
Kaya ayun!

01:01:57.000 --> 01:01:58.200
Akala ko kaya!

01:01:58.640 --> 01:02:00.280
Why is it this lousy temple again?

01:02:00.560 --> 01:02:02.120
You saw it all along,

01:02:02.320 --> 01:02:03.120
This is the plague god temple

01:02:03.120 --> 01:02:04.760
Where you killed old man wu!

01:02:05.360 --> 01:02:06.440
But you didn't dare expose it,

01:02:06.520 --> 01:02:07.920
Hindi dahil sa katapatan,

01:02:08.080 --> 01:02:09.720
But because you were afraid

01:02:09.760 --> 01:02:11.040
Your own crimes would be exposed too!

01:02:12.000 --> 01:02:13.440
Did you think hiding from each other

01:02:13.800 --> 01:02:16.000
Would let you survive in these troubled times?

01:02:31.400 --> 01:02:32.120
Ikaw...

01:02:32.960 --> 01:02:34.280
Hindi ka patay?

01:02:34.920 --> 01:02:36.160
Tian jinxiao!

01:02:38.560 --> 01:02:39.880
Do you think killing me

01:02:39.880 --> 01:02:41.960
Can cover up your gambling addiction,

01:02:42.080 --> 01:02:43.320
Embezzlement of military pay,

01:02:44.080 --> 01:02:46.360
And theft of property from plague victims?

01:02:46.360 --> 01:02:48.480
The relatives of those you ruined

01:02:48.480 --> 01:02:49.480
Matagal nang nagsumite

01:02:49.480 --> 01:02:52.240
Their complaints to the three judicial bodies!

01:02:53.680 --> 01:02:54.960
Hindi ka old man wu.

01:02:55.640 --> 01:02:57.080
You're that coffin maker!

01:02:57.800 --> 01:02:59.520
Then the wu shuang we saw...

01:03:06.280 --> 01:03:08.120
Sina shuang'er at xiao zhou ay pitumpung porsyentong magkamukha.

01:03:08.480 --> 01:03:09.240
Ito ay perpekto

01:03:09.680 --> 01:03:11.800
To make you guilty officials

01:03:11.960 --> 01:03:13.120
Gulat at gulo.

01:03:13.480 --> 01:03:16.880
Bawat krimen na pinagbibintangan niyo ngayon lang

01:03:16.880 --> 01:03:19.680
Malinaw na narinig ng tatlong judicial officials sa labas!

01:03:34.320 --> 01:03:35.400
Tapos na ang lahat!

01:03:36.760 --> 01:03:38.680
Bitawan mo ako! bitawan mo ako!

01:03:38.760 --> 01:03:40.080
My adoptive father is eunuch tian!

01:03:40.080 --> 01:03:41.440
How dare you touch me?

01:03:42.960 --> 01:03:44.640
Lord wu, iligtas mo ako!

01:03:45.280 --> 01:03:47.200
I... I'm willing to atone for my crimes!

01:03:47.600 --> 01:03:49.680
All their corruption ledgers!

01:03:49.680 --> 01:03:50.480
Ibibigay ko

01:03:50.480 --> 01:03:51.680
Manahimik ka, bastard!

01:03:52.160 --> 01:03:54.160
None of you three officials are good!

01:03:55.360 --> 01:03:56.560
Alam mo ba

01:03:56.560 --> 01:03:59.080
Who those rebels outside tongguan are now?

01:03:59.480 --> 01:04:02.760
They're the border soldiers you exploited,

01:04:03.080 --> 01:04:05.880
And the starving refugees from huazhou!

01:04:05.880 --> 01:04:08.480
If you officials hadn't

01:04:08.480 --> 01:04:10.520
Pushed the common people to this point,

01:04:11.200 --> 01:04:13.880
Would they have rebelled and become rebels?

01:04:23.440 --> 01:04:24.480
Ngayon lang,

01:04:25.480 --> 01:04:27.120
What tian jinxiao said

01:04:27.960 --> 01:04:29.320
Totoo lahat.

01:04:32.000 --> 01:04:33.600
You seized shuang'er,

01:04:34.480 --> 01:04:36.000
Pinatay siya,

01:04:36.280 --> 01:04:37.840
At kinulit siya!

01:04:38.600 --> 01:04:41.160
Please, for the sake of

01:04:43.120 --> 01:04:43.920
Itong matandang lalaki

01:04:44.920 --> 01:04:46.000
Having served the court for thirty years...

01:04:46.000 --> 01:04:47.840
Served the court for thirty years?

01:04:47.840 --> 01:04:50.240
You've tormented the people for thirty years!

01:04:50.600 --> 01:04:51.600
Ngayon,

01:04:52.080 --> 01:04:54.360
I want you to tell the truth

01:04:54.480 --> 01:04:56.040
In front of everyone,

01:04:56.040 --> 01:04:57.960
Eksakto tulad ng nangyari!

01:04:57.960 --> 01:04:59.960
Bigyan mo ng hustisya ang kapatid ko!

01:05:05.920 --> 01:05:07.240
Tindera,

01:05:08.480 --> 01:05:11.480
Do you happen to know an official named wu ling?

01:05:12.160 --> 01:05:12.960
Wu ling?

01:05:13.880 --> 01:05:14.760
Hindi kailanman narinig tungkol sa kanya.

01:05:15.080 --> 01:05:16.120
Hindi kailanman narinig tungkol sa kanya.

01:05:20.200 --> 01:05:21.440
Young master, pagbati.

01:05:22.080 --> 01:05:23.800
This humble girl wu shuang

01:05:23.800 --> 01:05:25.520
Is looking for my elder brother wu ling.

01:05:26.000 --> 01:05:27.640
He works in the city,

01:05:28.160 --> 01:05:30.160
But this is my first time here.

01:05:30.520 --> 01:05:32.320
I don't know where he is.

01:05:33.320 --> 01:05:34.480
Young lady, try somewhere else.

01:05:38.760 --> 01:05:40.320
This is from kind people.

01:05:40.800 --> 01:05:41.400
Kumain ng mabilis.

01:05:47.120 --> 01:05:48.960
Tatlong araw na kaming naghahanap pero wala.

01:05:49.280 --> 01:05:52.080
Do you think your brother really abandoned you?

01:05:54.040 --> 01:05:55.080
Hindi!

01:05:56.000 --> 01:05:57.800
My brother would never forget me!

01:05:59.040 --> 01:06:01.200
He's the best brother in the world!

01:06:02.240 --> 01:06:03.320
Sabi niya

01:06:04.080 --> 01:06:05.760
He'd bring us relief grain

01:06:06.040 --> 01:06:07.840
And told father and me to wait.

01:06:08.360 --> 01:06:10.360
I know i'll wait for him!

01:06:13.960 --> 01:06:15.560
A prosperous people make a strong nation.

01:06:15.800 --> 01:06:17.000
A nation is the state,

01:06:17.000 --> 01:06:19.080
And the people are us common folk!

01:06:20.320 --> 01:06:20.720
Magaling!

01:06:20.720 --> 01:06:21.120
Eto na.

01:06:28.320 --> 01:06:29.880
Handa na ang pansit!

01:06:30.720 --> 01:06:31.400
Siguradong nagugutom ka.

01:06:36.600 --> 01:06:37.800
Birthday mo ngayon.

01:06:38.120 --> 01:06:39.360
Dapat kumain ka ng dalawa.

01:06:41.800 --> 01:06:43.280
Ngayon, nararamdaman ko

01:06:43.360 --> 01:06:45.160
Parang emperador!

01:06:49.440 --> 01:06:50.440
Ngayong taon,

01:06:50.600 --> 01:06:52.200
We'll surely have a good harvest!

01:06:55.960 --> 01:06:56.640
Kuya!

01:06:57.920 --> 01:06:59.680
Father and i are waiting for you!

01:07:01.240 --> 01:07:02.720
My brother's name is wu ling.

01:07:02.720 --> 01:07:04.120
Nagtatrabaho siya sa lungsod.

01:07:04.560 --> 01:07:06.160
Alam mo ba kung nasaan siya?

01:07:06.160 --> 01:07:07.920
Dumiretso ka na.

01:07:07.920 --> 01:07:10.000
The prefecture yamen is around the corner.

01:07:10.360 --> 01:07:11.280
Tanong mo dyan.

01:07:11.280 --> 01:07:12.320
Salamat, uncle.

01:07:17.960 --> 01:07:18.880
Huminahon ka, panginoon.

01:07:19.480 --> 01:07:20.920
A common girl is asking to see you,

01:07:20.920 --> 01:07:22.240
Sinasabing hinahanap niya ang kanyang kapatid na nagtatrabaho dito.

01:07:22.240 --> 01:07:23.760
I didn't dare let her in without permission,

01:07:23.760 --> 01:07:25.080
So i told her to wait in the corridor.

01:07:26.080 --> 01:07:27.440
With the plague rampant these days,

01:07:27.440 --> 01:07:29.240
How dare you bring just anyone into the yamen?

01:07:31.200 --> 01:07:32.200
Ang iyong karangalan!

01:07:34.200 --> 01:07:35.080
Ang iyong karangalan!

01:07:35.320 --> 01:07:36.560
Maawa po kayo!

01:07:37.400 --> 01:07:40.120
Help me find my brother wu ling!

01:07:40.680 --> 01:07:42.000
Kung alam niya,

01:07:42.000 --> 01:07:44.120
He'll surely repay your great kindness!

01:07:46.920 --> 01:07:48.320
Dalhin mo siya.

01:08:10.840 --> 01:08:13.000
You seem quite engrossed, young lady.

01:08:15.120 --> 01:08:17.080
Thank you, your honor, for the clothes and soup.

01:08:23.359 --> 01:08:24.279
Oo nga pala,

01:08:24.720 --> 01:08:25.760
Sabi mo

01:08:26.279 --> 01:08:29.240
Your brother's name is wu ling.

01:08:30.800 --> 01:08:32.800
Saan siya nagtatrabaho?

01:08:33.200 --> 01:08:34.120
Ang iyong karangalan,

01:08:34.520 --> 01:08:36.160
I only know it's in huazhou.

01:08:36.279 --> 01:08:37.880
I don't know the exact camp.

01:08:38.800 --> 01:08:40.080
This humble girl doesn't know.

01:08:49.120 --> 01:08:51.640
You don't know which camp?

01:08:59.760 --> 01:09:01.880
What does your brother look like exactly?

01:09:02.160 --> 01:09:04.160
Halika, sabihin sa akin nang detalyado.

01:09:04.399 --> 01:09:05.279
Baka

01:09:05.520 --> 01:09:07.439
Nakita ko na siya somewhere.

01:09:08.800 --> 01:09:10.000
Kapatid ko...

01:09:14.840 --> 01:09:16.640
Umupo sa aking kandungan

01:09:17.240 --> 01:09:18.640
At dahan-dahang magsalita.

01:09:20.120 --> 01:09:21.040
Ang iyong karangalan,

01:09:21.560 --> 01:09:22.760
Please show some respect!

01:09:28.640 --> 01:09:30.880
Pinararangalan kita sa pamamagitan ng pagpapaupo sa iyo dito!

01:09:30.880 --> 01:09:32.680
Hindi mo ba pinapahalagahan ito?

01:09:37.439 --> 01:09:38.319
Bakit?

01:09:39.279 --> 01:09:41.439
Ayaw mo na bang makita ang kapatid mo?

01:09:46.240 --> 01:09:47.040
Halika dito!

01:09:49.279 --> 01:09:50.279
Halika dito!

01:09:53.399 --> 01:09:54.040
Mapangahas!

01:10:28.680 --> 01:10:29.720
Suwail!

01:10:29.760 --> 01:10:30.760
Suwail ka!

01:10:33.760 --> 01:10:34.480
Ang iyong karangalan!

01:10:37.560 --> 01:10:38.480
Ang babaeng ito

01:10:38.680 --> 01:10:39.840
May salot!

01:10:39.840 --> 01:10:41.160
Siya ay dapat na isang disaster star reincarnated!

01:10:41.360 --> 01:10:42.960
Sinubukan niya akong saktan!

01:10:42.960 --> 01:10:44.000
Nagsisinungaling ka!

01:10:44.680 --> 01:10:45.760
Walanghiya ka!

01:10:45.760 --> 01:10:47.160
Sinubukan mo akong asarin!

01:10:47.280 --> 01:10:47.960
Ikaw...

01:10:49.200 --> 01:10:50.560
How dare you frame this official?

01:10:50.840 --> 01:10:52.640
Tiyak na traydor din ang kapatid mo!

01:10:52.960 --> 01:10:53.480
Go!

01:10:53.840 --> 01:10:55.000
Subaybayan ang kinaroroonan ni wu ling!

01:10:55.000 --> 01:10:56.240
Hulihin at pugutan din ng ulo!

01:10:58.120 --> 01:10:59.000
Huwag mong hawakan ang kapatid ko!

01:10:59.400 --> 01:11:00.480
Pakiusap ko!

01:11:00.960 --> 01:11:03.040
Patayin mo ako o pahirapan hayaan mo lang siya!

01:11:03.120 --> 01:11:05.080
Hihingi ako ng tawad sayo!

01:11:07.600 --> 01:11:10.200
Sa tingin mo, makakatulong ba ang pagmamalimos?

01:11:11.040 --> 01:11:13.240
Ang iyong kapatid na si wu ling ay talagang isang taksil!

01:11:13.440 --> 01:11:14.880
Hindi ka rin mabubuhay!

01:11:15.240 --> 01:11:16.400
Hulihin mo si wu ling!

01:11:16.800 --> 01:11:17.520
Magmadali!

01:11:17.520 --> 01:11:18.560
Chen weishan!

01:11:20.400 --> 01:11:22.720
Kung maglakas-loob kang hawakan ng buhok sa ulo ng kapatid ko,

01:11:22.840 --> 01:11:24.160
Maging multo man ako,

01:11:24.160 --> 01:11:26.360
Kakaladkarin kita sa impyerno kasama ko!

01:11:26.360 --> 01:11:27.160
Ikaw...

01:11:27.400 --> 01:11:28.160
Bruha!

01:11:28.400 --> 01:11:29.560
How dare you threaten ang opisyal na ito?

01:11:29.760 --> 01:11:30.720
Magmadali!

01:11:30.720 --> 01:11:32.080
Chen weishan!

01:11:33.600 --> 01:11:35.280
Balatan kita ng buhay,

01:11:35.360 --> 01:11:36.400
Bunutin ang iyong mga litid,

01:11:36.400 --> 01:11:39.160
At gawin kang magdusa na mas masahol pa kaysa sa kamatayan!

01:11:41.760 --> 01:11:42.800
Bruha!

01:11:42.960 --> 01:11:43.880
Bruha!

01:11:45.240 --> 01:11:46.120
Bruha!

01:11:54.600 --> 01:11:56.720
Kahit maging multo ako,

01:11:56.720 --> 01:11:58.360
Hinding-hindi kita bibitawan!

01:11:58.680 --> 01:12:00.960
May mga batas pa rin ang tang dynasty!

01:12:01.160 --> 01:12:01.960
Isang tao!

01:12:03.400 --> 01:12:04.040
Dito!

01:12:04.440 --> 01:12:06.680
Ang babaeng ito ang pinagmumulan ng kaguluhan!

01:12:06.960 --> 01:12:07.920
Pugutan agad siya ng ulo!

01:12:07.920 --> 01:12:09.080
Itapon mo siya sa mass grave!

01:12:09.320 --> 01:12:09.960
Oo, sir!

01:12:10.600 --> 01:12:11.280
Ang iyong karangalan!

01:12:11.280 --> 01:12:12.880
Ayon sa batas, dapat siyang litisin muna!

01:12:13.080 --> 01:12:14.120
Napakasamang espiritu

01:12:14.360 --> 01:12:15.600
Hindi karapat-dapat sa mga legal na pamamaraan!

01:12:15.600 --> 01:12:16.680
Pugutan siya ng ulo!

01:12:16.680 --> 01:12:19.000
Mga mapaminsalang opisyal!

01:12:19.280 --> 01:12:21.000
Walang sinuman sa inyo ang mamamatay ng mabuting kamatayan!

01:12:21.000 --> 01:12:23.680
Ipaghihiganti ako ng kapatid ko!

01:12:26.920 --> 01:12:28.960
Lahat ng sinabi mo

01:12:29.760 --> 01:12:31.080
Totoo ba ang lahat?

01:12:31.960 --> 01:12:32.640
Ito...

01:12:33.240 --> 01:12:35.280
Ito... Ito ay totoo!

01:12:35.280 --> 01:12:36.520
Magsalita ng mas malakas!

01:12:36.520 --> 01:12:39.120
Hayaang marinig ito ng lahat ng mga tao!

01:12:40.440 --> 01:12:41.880
Totoo naman!

01:12:42.800 --> 01:12:43.600
Totoo naman!

01:12:43.840 --> 01:12:44.640
Totoo naman!

01:12:45.280 --> 01:12:46.440
Mangyaring, para sa kapakanan ng

01:12:46.440 --> 01:12:48.680
Ang matandang ito ay naglilingkod din sa tang dynasty...

01:12:49.160 --> 01:12:49.880
Ako...

01:12:50.240 --> 01:12:50.960
Ako...

01:13:02.080 --> 01:13:03.240
Silang tatlo

01:13:03.920 --> 01:13:05.720
Isang nilustay na butil ng relief,

01:13:05.720 --> 01:13:07.040
Nagpapalitaw ng salot;

01:13:07.280 --> 01:13:09.040
Ang isa ay nagnakaw ng suweldo sa militar,

01:13:09.040 --> 01:13:10.400
Pagpatay ng mga sundalo;

01:13:10.760 --> 01:13:13.120
Binalewala ng isa ang buhay ng tao,

01:13:13.120 --> 01:13:14.680
Pagpatay sa isang karaniwang babae!

01:13:14.680 --> 01:13:17.280
Malinaw kitang itinapon sa apoy at sinunog hanggang mamatay!

01:13:17.920 --> 01:13:19.560
Paano ka pa mabubuhay?

01:13:20.400 --> 01:13:21.600
Salamat sa iyo,

01:13:22.040 --> 01:13:25.040
Pansamantalang ipinahiram sa akin ni yama ang buhay na ito.

01:13:28.760 --> 01:13:32.360
Gusto mo bang malaman kung paano ako nakaligtas?

01:13:32.360 --> 01:13:34.400
Sa pagkakataong ito, ang militar ng border army ay nagbabayad

01:13:34.720 --> 01:13:37.280
Ay inilipat sa ating divine strategy army.

01:13:37.280 --> 01:13:38.560
Matapos maitayo ang kuwartel,

01:13:38.560 --> 01:13:39.560
Marami pa ring natitira.

01:13:39.840 --> 01:13:42.200
Perpektong ialay bilang pagpupugay sa iyo, aking panginoon.

01:13:42.600 --> 01:13:44.520
Mangyaring bilangin ito.

01:13:46.880 --> 01:13:48.120
Nahawakan ba ng maayos ang lahat?

01:13:51.040 --> 01:13:52.560
Matandang bastard!

01:13:53.640 --> 01:13:55.480
Gusto mo pang kumapit sa pilak sa libingan!

01:14:01.520 --> 01:14:05.120
Buksan mo! buksan mo! buksan mo!

01:14:06.720 --> 01:14:07.760
Tanga!

01:14:07.920 --> 01:14:08.960
Ang sarili mong mga personal na guwardiya

01:14:08.960 --> 01:14:10.680
Maglakas-loob na idemanda ka sa censorate!

01:14:10.760 --> 01:14:12.480
Anong uri ka ng central protector?

01:14:13.120 --> 01:14:14.440
Si wu ling iyon!

01:14:14.920 --> 01:14:15.880
Dapat siya yun!

01:14:16.760 --> 01:14:19.840
Mamaya, hubarin mo ang lahat ng gamit sa paglilibing sa matandang babaeng iyon!

01:14:19.840 --> 01:14:21.880
Mga hairpin, alahas, pilak na pulseras

01:14:22.360 --> 01:14:23.520
Walang iwanan!

01:14:23.800 --> 01:14:24.680
Heneral!

01:14:24.960 --> 01:14:26.440
Namatay ang matandang babae sa salot.

01:14:26.440 --> 01:14:27.640
Ayon sa mga regulasyon, dapat siyang ilibing nang malalim.

01:14:27.640 --> 01:14:28.560
Mga regulasyon? anong mga regulasyon?

01:14:28.800 --> 01:14:30.120
Ang katawan ay nakabalot sa tatlong layer ng linen

01:14:30.120 --> 01:14:31.160
At binudburan ng quicklime.

01:14:31.480 --> 01:14:32.640
Ito ay dapat na maiwasan ang salot.

01:14:33.280 --> 01:14:34.160
Kung maghahalungkat tayo ng ganito,

01:14:34.160 --> 01:14:34.600
Paano kung

01:14:34.600 --> 01:14:35.480
Paano kung ano?

01:14:35.560 --> 01:14:36.960
Ang aking mga salita ay ang mga regulasyon!

01:14:37.160 --> 01:14:37.760
Bilisan mo!

01:14:37.760 --> 01:14:38.720
Hindi ka ba natatakot sa baho?

01:14:39.000 --> 01:14:41.040
Bukas, sabihin kay hu banxian na gumawa ng tubig na talisman

01:14:41.040 --> 01:14:42.560
Para punasan ng mga kapatid ang kanilang sarili.

01:14:44.800 --> 01:14:46.080
Tinatrato ko siya ng maayos!

01:14:46.440 --> 01:14:47.680
Pero kinakagat niya ako sa likod!

01:14:47.680 --> 01:14:49.920
Kung hindi dahil nagpadala si lord tian ng babala nang maaga,

01:14:50.080 --> 01:14:50.720
Mayroon ka nang

01:14:50.720 --> 01:14:51.760
Kumakain ng steamed cornbread

01:14:51.760 --> 01:14:52.840
Sa kulungan ng ministry of justice ngayon din!

01:14:58.640 --> 01:14:59.280
Umalis ka sa daan!

01:15:00.400 --> 01:15:01.200
Sabi ko sayo

01:15:01.480 --> 01:15:02.880
Sinabi ko sa iyo na huwag idemanda ang emperador!

01:15:03.120 --> 01:15:04.560
Isipin ang iyong sariling negosyo!

01:15:06.400 --> 01:15:07.640
Hayaan mong sabihin ko sa iyo ito

01:15:07.840 --> 01:15:08.840
Sa huazhou,

01:15:08.840 --> 01:15:10.280
Ako ang batas!

01:15:11.040 --> 01:15:13.800
Aabutan ka ng karma sooner or later!

01:15:14.680 --> 01:15:15.640
Ayos lang!

01:15:15.640 --> 01:15:16.720
Maghihintay ako!

01:15:18.240 --> 01:15:19.480
Itapon siya sa sirang templo!

01:15:23.040 --> 01:15:23.840
Sandali lang!

01:15:36.720 --> 01:15:38.200
Ling'er!

01:15:41.560 --> 01:15:42.400
Ama!

01:15:43.160 --> 01:15:46.400
Akala ko hindi na kita makikita!

01:15:51.400 --> 01:15:52.240
Ama!

01:15:52.480 --> 01:15:54.720
Mula nang pumunta ka sa chang'an para maglingkod,

01:15:55.920 --> 01:15:58.960
Walang nangyari sa village!

01:15:59.800 --> 01:16:03.880
Kinain ng mga balang ang lahat ng mga punla sa bukid!

01:16:03.880 --> 01:16:05.960
Hiniling ko sa old scholar na sumulat sa iyo,

01:16:05.960 --> 01:16:07.560
Para tanungin ang mga nakatataas

01:16:08.800 --> 01:16:11.680
Kapag dumating ang butil ng relief!

01:16:12.120 --> 01:16:15.840
Sinabi nila na ang korte ay naglaan ng relief grain,

01:16:16.320 --> 01:16:18.320
Ngunit hindi ito dumating!

01:16:18.960 --> 01:16:21.280
Ang mga taganayon ay gutom na gutom!

01:16:21.280 --> 01:16:23.640
Pagkatapos ang kakaibang sakit na ito mula sa huazhou ay tumama,

01:16:23.640 --> 01:16:26.600
At ngayo'y halos walang natira sa nayon!

01:16:26.880 --> 01:16:28.600
Hindi na kinaya ni shuang'er,

01:16:28.800 --> 01:16:31.160
Kaya nagpunta siya sa lungsod para humingi ng tulong sa iyo!

01:16:33.320 --> 01:16:34.000
Ama!

01:16:34.240 --> 01:16:35.520
Nasaan si shuang'er?

01:16:37.160 --> 01:16:38.200
Okay lang ba si shuang'er?

01:16:42.400 --> 01:16:45.040
Yung matandang asong si chen weishan!

01:16:45.760 --> 01:16:48.640
Nang makita niyang hindi infected si shuang'er,

01:16:48.920 --> 01:16:51.200
Nakakakuha siya ng masasamang pag-iisip!

01:16:51.200 --> 01:16:53.560
Ang opisyal ng asong iyon na si chen weishan

01:16:53.560 --> 01:16:54.480
Maling inakusahan siya bilang pinagmulan ng salot ，

01:16:54.480 --> 01:16:55.440
Pinatay siya!

01:16:55.840 --> 01:16:56.800
At ang aking ama

01:16:56.800 --> 01:16:59.280
Bilang nag-iisang saksi kay yang zhizhi na nangungurakot ng relief grain

01:16:59.280 --> 01:17:01.520
At pagpatay ng mga inosenteng tao,

01:17:01.600 --> 01:17:03.680
Brutal ding pinatahimik!

01:17:03.680 --> 01:17:06.680
Bakit hindi nagpadala ang korte ng relief grain?

01:17:07.040 --> 01:17:08.600
Bakit hindi ka nahawa?

01:17:09.280 --> 01:17:11.840
Bakit buhay ka pa?

01:17:12.000 --> 01:17:13.760
Aso kang opisyal!

01:17:13.760 --> 01:17:14.520
Hayaan mo na!

01:17:16.560 --> 01:17:18.400
Pupunta ako sa korte para kasuhan ka!

01:17:18.520 --> 01:17:20.640
Idedemanda kita!

01:17:20.760 --> 01:17:22.440
Hindi pa ito tapos!

01:17:26.160 --> 01:17:27.680
Maswerteng nakaligtas si tatay.

01:17:28.240 --> 01:17:30.160
Nang magising si ama,

01:17:30.160 --> 01:17:31.680
Napagtanto ko

01:17:31.840 --> 01:17:34.400
Lahat ng umuubo sa lungsod,

01:17:34.400 --> 01:17:36.560
Lahat ng nahawaan ng sakit,

01:17:36.760 --> 01:17:38.240
Ay parang ama

01:17:38.920 --> 01:17:40.800
Nakakulong sa sirang templong ito

01:17:41.160 --> 01:17:43.320
Ng mga ito, na binansagan bilang mga halimaw!

01:17:46.920 --> 01:17:48.400
Ang templong iyon ay nasa labas ng lungsod, tama ba?

01:17:48.640 --> 01:17:50.200
Sunugin ito kasama ang lahat sa loob!

01:17:50.560 --> 01:17:51.520
Walang iwan na buhay!

01:17:52.040 --> 01:17:52.880
Ama!

01:17:52.880 --> 01:17:53.520
Hindi!

01:17:58.760 --> 01:17:59.400
Shoot!

01:18:20.960 --> 01:18:21.440
Ama!

01:18:21.440 --> 01:18:22.520
Kailangan nating mag-break out!

01:18:27.680 --> 01:18:28.400
Ama!

01:18:30.440 --> 01:18:31.200
Ama!

01:18:35.720 --> 01:18:36.320
Ama!

01:18:36.600 --> 01:18:37.280
Ama!

01:18:37.680 --> 01:18:38.600
Ling'er!

01:18:38.760 --> 01:18:39.440
Ama!

01:18:39.960 --> 01:18:41.840
Mabuhay nang maayos!

01:18:42.160 --> 01:18:43.560
Maghiganti shuang'er,

01:18:44.120 --> 01:18:48.480
Ipaghiganti ang lahat ng mga tagabaryo na namatay!

01:18:51.400 --> 01:18:52.360
Ama!

01:19:11.240 --> 01:19:12.040
Gising ka na!

01:19:12.720 --> 01:19:14.320
Ikaw ba ang wu ling

01:19:14.840 --> 01:19:16.040
Sino ang pumasok sa censorate para idemanda ang emperador?

01:19:16.800 --> 01:19:18.040
Nasaan... Nasaan ang aking ama?

01:19:18.040 --> 01:19:19.000
Nasaan ang aking ama?

01:19:19.000 --> 01:19:20.080
Ang iyong ama ay pumanaw na.

01:19:20.720 --> 01:19:21.840
Pagdating namin,

01:19:21.840 --> 01:19:24.360
Nagawa ka lang naming ilabas sa apoy.

01:19:29.440 --> 01:19:31.720
Qiu ran, chief ng detective bureau ng chang'an.

01:19:32.800 --> 01:19:33.920
Bakit mo ako niligtas?

01:19:34.200 --> 01:19:36.200
Bagama't kumikilos ang mga detektib sa dilim,

01:19:36.320 --> 01:19:37.440
Nakatago sa liwanag ng araw,

01:19:37.960 --> 01:19:38.920
Ngunit

01:19:38.920 --> 01:19:41.920
Dalubhasa sa pagwawasto ng mga maling hindi pinapansin ng mundo.

01:19:43.120 --> 01:19:44.720
Gusto mo bang ipaghiganti ang iyong ama,

01:19:44.920 --> 01:19:45.880
Ipaghiganti mo ang iyong kapatid,

01:19:46.560 --> 01:19:50.320
At humingi ng hustisya para sa mga taganayon na sinunog hanggang mamatay?

01:19:56.280 --> 01:19:57.280
Samahan mo kami.

01:19:58.400 --> 01:20:00.280
Ipaalam sa mga tiwaling opisyal na iyon

01:20:01.080 --> 01:20:02.040
Na sa great tang,

01:20:02.560 --> 01:20:04.080
Umiiral pa rin ang hustisya!

01:20:04.280 --> 01:20:05.280
Mula sa araw na iyon,

01:20:05.520 --> 01:20:06.880
Wala na si wu ling.

01:20:07.160 --> 01:20:08.880
Tanging si ye xiao, ang detective.

01:20:09.240 --> 01:20:11.400
Noong panahong iyon, laganap ang alingawngaw ng masasamang espiritu sa huazhou.

01:20:11.640 --> 01:20:12.480
Ang anak ng langit

01:20:12.480 --> 01:20:14.080
Personal na inutusan si wang shao ng imperial bodyguards

01:20:14.080 --> 01:20:15.920
At ako upang malutas ang misteryo sa loob ng pitong araw,

01:20:15.960 --> 01:20:17.160
Para malinis ang pangalan ng pamilya ko.

01:20:17.680 --> 01:20:18.640
Kasuklam-suklam!

01:20:18.880 --> 01:20:20.840
Kayong grupo ng mga taksil na nagpapabor sa mga bating

01:20:21.320 --> 01:20:23.160
Ang landas ng hustisya ay puno ng mga hadlang!

01:20:24.200 --> 01:20:25.920
Nagdala ka ng kahihiyan sa divine strategy army!

01:20:26.480 --> 01:20:28.080
Wala kaming choice kundi itakda itong makamulto na bitag,

01:20:28.320 --> 01:20:30.360
Sa wakas ay naakit ka upang ipakita ang iyong tunay na kulay.

01:20:30.680 --> 01:20:32.240
Ngayon, kasama ang tatlong judicial bodies dito,

01:20:32.240 --> 01:20:34.040
Ang ebidensiya laban sa iyo ay hindi masasagot.

01:20:34.040 --> 01:20:35.280
Walang paraan para makatakas!

01:20:38.960 --> 01:20:41.120
Bagama't matagal nang gumaling ang kakaibang sakit,

01:20:42.120 --> 01:20:43.960
Ang puso ng mga tao

01:20:44.200 --> 01:20:46.560
Ay pinukaw ng inyong mga salarin.

01:20:46.920 --> 01:20:47.840
Ngayon,

01:20:48.480 --> 01:20:50.200
Hinatulan ka ng kamatayan sa pamamagitan ng pagpugot ng ulo.

01:20:50.520 --> 01:20:52.320
Dito mismo, sa harap ng plague god temple,

01:20:52.320 --> 01:20:53.880
Sa ilalim ng langit at lupa!

01:20:54.560 --> 01:20:55.680
Execution agad!

01:20:55.680 --> 01:20:56.800
Para bigyan ng babala ang iba,

01:20:56.800 --> 01:20:58.120
At para mapawi ang galit ng publiko!

01:20:58.320 --> 01:20:59.640
Kayong tatlong tiwaling opisyal

01:20:59.640 --> 01:21:01.280
May last words ka ba?

01:21:11.360 --> 01:21:12.360
Ipatupad!

01:21:17.520 --> 01:21:18.240
Pugutan ng ulo!

01:21:19.880 --> 01:21:21.880
Magaling! magaling! magaling!

01:21:21.880 --> 01:21:32.800
Buti napugutan ng ulo! buti napugutan ng ulo! buti napugutan ng ulo!

01:21:33.200 --> 01:21:34.360
Pagpugot sa tatlong taksil na ito

01:21:35.840 --> 01:21:37.160
Upang pasalamatan ang langit,

01:21:38.360 --> 01:21:39.760
At para aliwin ang mga patay!

01:21:40.760 --> 01:21:41.560
Ama!

01:21:42.560 --> 01:21:43.320
Shuang'er!

01:21:45.880 --> 01:21:46.720
Ling'er!

01:21:48.000 --> 01:21:49.480
Naipaghiganti na kita!

01:21:49.920 --> 01:21:50.640
Ama!

01:21:51.080 --> 01:21:53.000
Sabi ni kuya pagdating ng relief grain,

01:21:53.640 --> 01:21:54.640
Gagawin natin

01:21:55.280 --> 01:21:57.200
Magtanim ng kalahating ektarya ng trigo!

